{
  "stem": "20710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went, we slept through I think two or three nights in this-- in this in this room, this building that they reserved for the people, for these, you know, remnants, who were left, and then-- to have someplace to come in.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then-- and then we started going back to Hanaczow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How long a distance was it from Lwow to Hanaczow?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was but, maybe, 35 to maybe more of miles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there was going in miles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Miles were-- I mean, kilometers and miles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't remember how many kilometers to-- to-- to-- to-- but anyway, it was quite a distance.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there's also-- there was a train from Kurowice to-- to Lwow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But not from Hanaczow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the trains didn't go that time, and this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [SIGHS] we-- [SIGHS] we try to get back to Hanaczow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we try to walk again, I with my cousin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we walked, you know, till it starts getting dark, and then we stopped in another village that we-- we happened to be, the year before, there for awhile.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they burned down Hanaczow, we went there and we-- we stayed there for awhile.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What village was this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bilka.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bilka, [NON-ENGLISH], something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stopped there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this cousin of my had a-- had a-- a family that they-- she stayed with them, gentiles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we came in there and she received us very nice and she gave us something to eat and we slept through the night.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then in the morning, we were ready to-- to proceed to go to Hanaczow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And while we left her house and-- and we were, you know, getting ready to go to the main road, there were Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they-- they were cruising around with big trucks.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
